{"word":"Elijah","slug":"elijah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Elijah</b> - the prophet<p/><b>(1)</b> General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=1'>1Ki 17:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=15'>1Ki 17:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=23'>1Ki 17:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=21'>1Ki 18:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=5'>1Ki 19:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=19'>1Ki 19:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=17'>1Ki 21:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=1&verse=3'>2Ki 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=1&verse=10'>2Ki 1:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=2&verse=11'>2Ki 2:11</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=12'>2Ch 21:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=4&verse=5'>Mal 4:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=3'>Mat 17:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=26'>Luk 4:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=54'>Luk 9:54</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=5&verse=17'>Jas 5:17</a><p/>---Summary of his life<p/>---Three times fed with Divine Supplies<p/>--By Ravens<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=6'>1Ki 17:6</a><p/>--By miraculously increased store of the widow<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=15'>1Ki 17:15</a><p/>--By an angel<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=5'>1Ki 19:5-8</a><p/>A fearless reformer<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=17'>1Ki 18:17-40</a><p/>Rebuked kings<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=20'>1Ki 21:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=1&verse=16'>2Ki 1:16</a><p/>Mighty in prayer<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=20'>1Ki 17:20-22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=36'>1Ki 18:36-38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=5&verse=17'>Jas 5:17</a><p/>In one instance yielded to discouragement<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=3'>1Ki 19:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=4'>1Ki 19:4</a><p/>Not infallible in judgment<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=14'>1Ki 19:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=18'>1Ki 19:18</a><p/>Divinely honoured<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=2&verse=11'>2Ki 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=3'>Mat 17:3</a><p/>---, Miracles of. See MIRACLES<p/><b>(2) Prophecies </b>of<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=1'>1Ki 17:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=19'>1Ki 21:19-24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=1&verse=2'>2Ki 1:2-17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=25'>2Ki 9:25-37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=12'>2Ch 21:12-15</a>"}]}